command to generate a component
--------------------------------

ng generate component   <componentname>
ng generate component   folderpath/<componentname>
ng g c   folderpath/<componentname>  shorthand
since we have not installed angular particualar version globally we will use npx way of creating component

npx @angular/cli@19 generate component 

